title: The Best Of The Dan Patrick Show
itunes:title: The Best Of The Dan Patrick Show
description:
On today's Dan Patrick Show, DP recaps last night's Giants/Cowboys game. Are we overreacting to Cooper Rush's performance? Dan Le Batard, host of the Dan Le Batard Show, joins us to talk positively about Dolphins football. Is he in on Tua? And former NFL Linebacker Clay Matthews tells us whether or not he's officially retired.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
